{"title":"红色的纸包","authors":["夏萍"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":12,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的纸包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我被批准入劳动大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺信一封又一封来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当和同志们分别的前夕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收到一个红色的纸包。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是“7”字形的红色纸包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面有两行金字闪耀："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“预祝你下去丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待你传来喜报！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开这沉甸甸的纸包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面是一把明亮的镰刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要用镰刀收割新粮食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要用镰刀把旧思想割掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（辽宁阜新）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}